methods.name: showAndImport
methods.comment:
Shows the batch import dialog (via runSwingLater) and prompts the user to select
 a file if the supplied  is empty.
 
 The dialog will chain to the ImportBatchTask when the user clicks the
 OK button.

params.name: tool
params.comment: PluginTool that will be the parent of the dialog

params.name: batchInfo
params.comment: optional BatchInfo instance with already discovered applications, or null.

params.name: initialFiles
params.comment: optional List of FSRL to add to the batch import dialog, or null.

params.name: defaultFolder
params.comment: optional default destination folder for imported files or null for root folder.

params.name: programManager
params.comment:
optional ProgramManager that will be used to open the newly imported
 binaries.
